::Battera::

She didn't recognize the name Magmatron.  She still felt nervous.
"Well,ok then.  I'll go with you.  But once my wing is fixed, I'm gone. OUt 
of there.  Go it? I'm not hanging around to get myself killed."
"BATTERA, TERRORIZE!" she transformed into her bot mode.  She started to 
walk away when she got the idea that she  had no clue as th where the base 
was.  She turned around and walked back to Cybershark.
"Uh, where is this base of your's?"

::CyberShark::

    He could see the nervousness in her eyes as she asked who his commander 
is. Who does she fear? He thought to himself.
"My commander is Magmatron. He is new to this planet and he has offered 
sanctuary to anyone who needs it." CyberShark said.
